{
  "stem": "17426.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 83.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Richard Grimm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Muselmann was our term for someone who is about to be the next one to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had cheekbones, no flesh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had eyes, but couldn't see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had feet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And hands that were hanging down just limply.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a muselmann.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how this term was born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But suddenly, it was born and it was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The closest that I can relate to is probably nomads in the Sahara, the desert, hungry and thirsty and depleted of strength.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those were Muslims.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's why Muslim German, the muselmann, Muslim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And probably that's the best that I can guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it's only a guess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In any event, he I said to him, Richard, I can do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If you just let me, I can do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just need to be washed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I need a bath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I need a little cream on my hands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My hands were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My hands were calloused.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I need to be just restored to what I was in Gutenbrunn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, I'll see what I can do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were other dentists in [INAUDIBLE], much more qualified than I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was just so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was just so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The following morning, when I was staying in line to be [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] taken to the coal mine, I heard him calling my name.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The dentist, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] forwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I ran over with all the strength that I had, I stopped six feet in front of the lager-- at the lagerfuhrer, who was Otto Moll, a man whose cruelty can never be adequately described.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And Richard said to him, this was our dentist in Gutenbrunn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he sort of endorsed me with a couple of words that I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
